<Routines>
<Routine Name="Logic" Type="RLL">
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(ReadStartCmd)ONS(ReadOns.0)RES(TimeMeassure)MOV(5,ReadSeq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="1" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Initialize parameters
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Initialize parameters
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(ReadSeq,5)MOV(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].Counter,ReadEntryCounter)MOV(0,ReadArrayElement)FLL(0,OUT[0],2000)FLL(0,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Data[0],112)MOV(10,ReadSeq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="2" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Check Array Elements
If NumOfBytes Equal  0 then Error or done
If NumOfBytes Not Equal to 0 then perform Writing - Copy values to actuel writing
If StartByte plus Number Of bytes greater than TagSize then Error.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Check Array Elements
If NumOfBytes Equal  0 then Error or done
If NumOfBytes Not Equal to 0 then perform Writing - Copy values to actuel writing
If StartByte plus Number Of bytes greater than TagSize then Error.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(ReadSeq,10)[GRT(ReadArray.NumOfBytes[ReadArrayElement],0) MOV(ReadArray.StartByte[ReadArrayElement],ReadStartByte) MOV(ReadArray.NumOfBytes[ReadArrayElement],ReadNumOfBytes) MOV(15,ReadSeq) ,EQU(ReadArray.NumOfBytes[ReadArrayElement],0) MOV(300,ReadSeq) ,ADD(ReadStartByte,ReadNumOfBytes,ReadEndByte) GRT(ReadEndByte,TagSize) MOV(200,ReadSeq) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="3" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Initialize parameters to RFID module
Calculate Number of cycles to run for doing complete reading

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Initialize parameters to RFID module
Calculate Number of cycles to run for doing complete reading

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(ReadSeq,15)[LEQ(ReadNumOfBytes,112) MOV(1,CalcNumOfReadCycles) MOV(0,ReadNumOfByteRemaining) ,GRT(ReadNumOfBytes,112) DIV(ReadNumOfBytes,112,CalcNumOfReadCycles) MOD(ReadNumOfBytes,112,ReadNumOfByteRemaining) ]MOV(1,Act_ReadCycles)MOV(20,ReadSeq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="4" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Copy StartByte and Lenght Values to Command register To RFID module
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Copy StartByte and Lenght Values to Command register To RFID module
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(ReadSeq,20)[EQU(Act_ReadCycles,1) [LEQ(ReadNumOfBytes,112) MOV(ReadStartByte,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Address) MOV(ReadNumOfBytes,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Length) ,GRT(ReadNumOfBytes,112) MOV(ReadStartByte,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Address) MOV(112,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Length) ] ,GRT(Act_ReadCycles,1) [LEQ(Act_ReadCycles,CalcNumOfReadCycles) CPT(ReadStartByte_Cmd,((Act_ReadCycles-1)*112)+ReadStartByte) MOV(ReadStartByte_Cmd,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Address) MOV(112,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Length) ,GRT(Act_ReadCycles,CalcNumOfReadCycles) CPT(ReadStartByte_Cmd,((CalcNumOfReadCycles)*112)+ReadStartByte) MOV(ReadStartByte_Cmd,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Address) MOV(ReadNumOfByteRemaining,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Length) ] ]MOV(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].Counter,ReadEntryCounter)MOV(30,ReadSeq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="5" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Copy Additional Command values to command register of RFID Module
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Copy Additional Command values to command register of RFID Module
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(ReadSeq,30)MOV(UIDHi,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].UIDHi)MOV(UIDLow,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].UIDLow)MOV(750,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Timeout)MOV(0,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Command)MOV(40,ReadSeq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="6" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Look for Command equal Zero in Input Part of Command Register 
If Equal to Zero Module is ready to receive new command
Set reading commad to Module ( command = 4)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Look for Command equal Zero in Input Part of Command Register 
If Equal to Zero Module is ready to receive new command
Set reading commad to Module ( command = 4)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(ReadSeq,40)EQU(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].Command,0)MOV(4,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Command)MOV(50,ReadSeq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="7" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Look for Busy signal from Module to see command is processing
Here using change in CounterValue detecting as busy signal
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Look for Busy signal from Module to see command is processing
Here using change in CounterValue detecting as busy signal
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(ReadSeq,50)NEQ(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].Counter,ReadEntryCounter)MOV(60,ReadSeq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="8" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Busy Off meaning Reading done when Reading Command  "4" is in Command Input Area

Reset Reading Command 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Busy Off meaning Reading done when Reading Command  "4" is in Command Input Area

Reset Reading Command 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(ReadSeq,60)XIO(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].Busy)EQU(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].Command,4)MOV(0,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Command)MOV(65,ReadSeq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="9" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Copy StartByte and Lenght Values to Command register From RFID module
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Copy StartByte and Lenght Values to Command register From RFID module
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(ReadSeq,65)[EQU(Act_ReadCycles,1) [LEQ(ReadNumOfBytes,112) CPS(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].Data[0],OUT[ReadStartByte],ReadNumOfBytes) ,GRT(ReadNumOfBytes,112) CPS(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].Data[0],OUT[ReadStartByte],112) ] ,GRT(Act_ReadCycles,1) [LEQ(Act_ReadCycles,CalcNumOfReadCycles) CPT(ReadStartByte_Cmd,((Act_ReadCycles-1)*112)+ReadStartByte) CPS(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].Data[0],OUT[ReadStartByte_Cmd],112) ,GRT(Act_ReadCycles,CalcNumOfReadCycles) CPT(ReadStartByte_Cmd,((CalcNumOfReadCycles)*112)+ReadStartByte) CPS(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].Data[0],OUT[ReadStartByte_Cmd],ReadNumOfByteRemaining) ] ]MOV(70,ReadSeq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="10" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Check if Number of Reading cycles is done
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Check if Number of Reading cycles is done
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(ReadSeq,70)[MOV(100,ReadSeq) ,[LES(Act_ReadCycles,CalcNumOfReadCycles) ,EQU(Act_ReadCycles,CalcNumOfReadCycles) NEQ(ReadNumOfByteRemaining,0) ] ADD(Act_ReadCycles,1,Act_ReadCycles) MOV(20,ReadSeq) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="11" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Add number in array elements to start writing from next Array Element
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Add number in array elements to start writing from next Array Element
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(ReadSeq,100)ONS(ReadOns.1)ADD(ReadArrayElement,1,ReadArrayElement)[LEQ(ReadArrayElement,9) MOV(10,ReadSeq) ,GRT(ReadArrayElement,9) MOV(300,ReadSeq) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="12" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Writing Done
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Writing Done
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(ReadSeq,300)OTE(DN);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="13" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Timer for Meassurering Writing Time
Loosing Tag during Write resulting in Error.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Timer for Meassurering Writing Time
Loosing Tag during Write resulting in Error.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[LIM(5,ReadSeq,70)[OTE(IP) TON(TimeMeassure,?,?) ,MOV(TimeMeassure.ACC,ReadingTime) ,[XIO(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].TagPresent) ONS(ReadOns.2) ,XIC(TimeMeassure.DN) ONS(ReadOns.7) ] MOV(200,ReadSeq) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="14" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
A Fault has occured during reading 
Except error 11 and 15 witch is hardware fault -> they will issue a fault when enabled.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
A Fault has occured during reading 
Except error 11 and 15 witch is hardware fault -> they will issue a fault when enabled.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[[XIC(ReadStartCmd) NEQ(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].ChError,0) ,EQU(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].ChError,11) ,EQU(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].ChError,15) ]TON(ErrorTime,?,?)XIC(ErrorTime.DN)ONS(ReadOns.6)MOV(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].ChError,ERROR)MOV(200,ReadSeq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="15" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Writing Faulted
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Writing Faulted
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(ReadSeq,200)OTE(ER);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="16" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Reset All Tags when Start Commad resets
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Reset All Tags when Start Commad resets
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIO(ReadStartCmd)ONS(ReadOns.3)MOV(0,Act_ReadCycles)MOV(0,ReadStartByte)MOV(0,ReadNumOfBytes)MOV(0,ReadingTime)MOV(0,ReadArrayElement)MOV(0,ReadOns)MOV(0,ReadEntryCounter)MOV(0,ReadSeq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="17" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Reset In Command by active Error
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Reset In Command by active Error
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(ResetIn)XIC(ER)ONS(ReadOns.4)MOV(5,AOI_Seq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="18" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Reset All Output command to Module
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Reset All Output command to Module
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(AOI_Seq,5)ONS(ReadOns.5)[MOV(0,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Address) ,MOV(0,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Length) ,MOV(0,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Timeout) ,MOV(0,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Data[0]) ,MOV(0,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].UIDHi) ,MOV(0,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].UIDLow) ,MOV(0,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Command) ,MOV(0,ERROR) ]OTL(RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Reset)MOV(10,AOI_Seq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="19" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Wait for the interface to see a 0 in the command word, then load a value of 41.  The time it takes the interface to see a 0 value is directly related to the RPI of the interface.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Wait for the interface to see a 0 in the command word, then load a value of 41.  The time it takes the interface to see a 0 value is directly related to the RPI of the interface.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(AOI_Seq,10)XIC(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].Reset)OTU(RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Reset)MOV(100,AOI_Seq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
</Routines>
