<Routines>
<Routine Name="Logic" Type="RLL">
<RLLContent>
<Rung Number="0" Type="N">
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(WriteStartCmd)ONS(WriteOns.0)RES(TimeMeassure)MOV(5,WriteSeq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="1" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Initialize parameters
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Initialize parameters
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(WriteSeq,5)MOV(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].Counter,WriteEntryCounter)MOV(0,WriteArrayElement)MOV(10,WriteSeq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="2" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Check Array Elements
If NumOfBytes Equal  0 then Error or done
If NumOfBytes Not Equal to 0 then perform Writing - Copy values to actuel writing
If StartByte plus Number Of bytes greater than TagSize then Error.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Check Array Elements
If NumOfBytes Equal  0 then Error or done
If NumOfBytes Not Equal to 0 then perform Writing - Copy values to actuel writing
If StartByte plus Number Of bytes greater than TagSize then Error.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(WriteSeq,10)[GRT(WriteArray.NumOfBytes[WriteArrayElement],0) MOV(WriteArray.StartByte[WriteArrayElement],WriteStartByte) MOV(WriteArray.NumOfBytes[WriteArrayElement],WriteNumOfBytes) MOV(15,WriteSeq) ,EQU(WriteArray.NumOfBytes[WriteArrayElement],0) MOV(300,WriteSeq) ,ADD(WriteStartByte,WriteNumOfBytes,WriteEndByte) GRT(WriteEndByte,TagSize) MOV(200,WriteSeq) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="3" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Initialize parameters to RFID module
Calculate Number of cycles to run for doing complete writing

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Initialize parameters to RFID module
Calculate Number of cycles to run for doing complete writing

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(WriteSeq,15)[LEQ(WriteNumOfBytes,112) MOV(1,CalcNumOfWriteCycles) MOV(0,WriteNumOfByteRemaining) ,GRT(WriteNumOfBytes,112) DIV(WriteNumOfBytes,112,CalcNumOfWriteCycles) MOD(WriteNumOfBytes,112,WriteNumOfByteRemaining) ]MOV(1,Act_WriteCycles)MOV(20,WriteSeq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="4" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Copy StartByte and Lenght Values to Command register To RFID module
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Copy StartByte and Lenght Values to Command register To RFID module
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(WriteSeq,20)[EQU(Act_WriteCycles,1) [LEQ(WriteNumOfBytes,112) CPS(IN[WriteStartByte],RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Data[0],WriteNumOfBytes) MOV(WriteStartByte,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Address) MOV(WriteNumOfBytes,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Length) ,GRT(WriteNumOfBytes,112) CPS(IN[WriteStartByte],RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Data[0],112) MOV(WriteStartByte,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Address) MOV(112,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Length) ] ,GRT(Act_WriteCycles,1) [LEQ(Act_WriteCycles,CalcNumOfWriteCycles) CPT(WriteStartByte_Cmd,((Act_WriteCycles-1)*112)+WriteStartByte) CPS(IN[WriteStartByte_Cmd],RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Data[0],112) MOV(WriteStartByte_Cmd,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Address) MOV(112,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Length) ,GRT(Act_WriteCycles,CalcNumOfWriteCycles) CPT(WriteStartByte_Cmd,((CalcNumOfWriteCycles)*112)+WriteStartByte) CPS(IN[WriteStartByte_Cmd],RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Data[0],WriteNumOfByteRemaining) MOV(WriteStartByte_Cmd,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Address) MOV(WriteNumOfByteRemaining,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Length) ] ]MOV(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].Counter,WriteEntryCounter)MOV(30,WriteSeq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="5" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Copy Additional Command values to command register of RFID Module
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Copy Additional Command values to command register of RFID Module
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(WriteSeq,30)MOV(UIDHi,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].UIDHi)MOV(UIDLow,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].UIDLow)MOV(750,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Timeout)MOV(0,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Command)MOV(40,WriteSeq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="6" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Look for Command equal Zero in Input Part of Command Register 
If Equal to Zero Module is ready to receive new command
Set writing commad to Module ( command =14)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Look for Command equal Zero in Input Part of Command Register 
If Equal to Zero Module is ready to receive new command
Set writing commad to Module ( command =14)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(WriteSeq,40)EQU(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].Command,0)MOV(14,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Command)MOV(50,WriteSeq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="7" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Look for Busy signal from Module to see command is processing
Here using change in CounterValue detecting as busy signal
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Look for Busy signal from Module to see command is processing
Here using change in CounterValue detecting as busy signal
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(WriteSeq,50)NEQ(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].Counter,WriteEntryCounter)MOV(60,WriteSeq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="8" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Busy Off meaning Writing done when Writing Command  "14" is in Command Input Area

Reset Writing Command 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Busy Off meaning Writing done when Writing Command  "14" is in Command Input Area

Reset Writing Command 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(WriteSeq,60)XIO(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].Busy)EQU(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].Command,14)MOV(0,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Command)MOV(70,WriteSeq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="9" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Check if Number of Writing cycles is done
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Check if Number of Writing cycles is done
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(WriteSeq,70)[MOV(100,WriteSeq) ,[LES(Act_WriteCycles,CalcNumOfWriteCycles) ,EQU(Act_WriteCycles,CalcNumOfWriteCycles) NEQ(WriteNumOfByteRemaining,0) ] ADD(Act_WriteCycles,1,Act_WriteCycles) MOV(20,WriteSeq) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="10" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Add number in array elements to start writing from next Array Element
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Add number in array elements to start writing from next Array Element
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(WriteSeq,100)ONS(WriteOns.1)ADD(WriteArrayElement,1,WriteArrayElement)[LEQ(WriteArrayElement,9) MOV(10,WriteSeq) ,GRT(WriteArrayElement,9) MOV(300,WriteSeq) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="11" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Writing Done
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Writing Done
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(WriteSeq,300)OTE(DN);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="12" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Timer for Meassurering Writing Time
Loosing Tag during Write resulting in Error.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Timer for Meassurering Writing Time
Loosing Tag during Write resulting in Error.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[LIM(5,WriteSeq,70)[OTE(IP) TON(TimeMeassure,?,?) ,MOV(TimeMeassure.ACC,WritingTime) ,[XIO(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].TagPresent) ONS(WriteOns.2) ,XIC(TimeMeassure.DN) ONS(WriteOns.7) ] MOV(200,WriteSeq) ];]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="13" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
A Fault has occured during writing 
Except error 11 and 15 witch is hardware fault -> they will issue a fault when enabled.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
A Fault has occured during writing 
Except error 11 and 15 witch is hardware fault -> they will issue a fault when enabled.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[[XIC(WriteStartCmd) NEQ(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].ChError,0) ,EQU(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].ChError,11) ,EQU(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].ChError,15) ]TON(ErrorTime,?,?)XIC(ErrorTime.DN)ONS(WriteOns.6)MOV(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].ChError,ERROR)MOV(200,WriteSeq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="14" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Writing Faulted
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Writing Faulted
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(WriteSeq,200)OTE(ER);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="15" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Reset All Tags when Start Commad resets
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Reset All Tags when Start Commad resets
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIO(WriteStartCmd)ONS(WriteOns.3)MOV(0,Act_WriteCycles)MOV(0,WriteStartByte)MOV(0,WriteNumOfBytes)MOV(0,WritingTime)MOV(0,WriteArrayElement)MOV(0,WriteOns)MOV(0,WriteEntryCounter)MOV(0,WriteSeq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="16" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Reset In Command by active Error
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Reset In Command by active Error
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[XIC(ResetIn)XIC(ER)ONS(WriteOns.4)MOV(5,AOI_Seq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="17" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Reset All Output command to Module
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Reset All Output command to Module
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(AOI_Seq,5)ONS(WriteOns.5)[MOV(0,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Address) ,MOV(0,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Length) ,MOV(0,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Timeout) ,MOV(0,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Data[0]) ,MOV(0,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].UIDHi) ,MOV(0,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].UIDLow) ,MOV(0,RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Command) ,MOV(0,ERROR) ]OTL(RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Reset)MOV(10,AOI_Seq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
<Rung Number="18" Type="N">
<Comment>
<![CDATA[-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Wait for the interface to see a 0 in the command word, then load a value of 41.  The time it takes the interface to see a 0 value is directly related to the RPI of the interface.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
<LocalizedComment Lang="en-US">
<![CDATA[-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Wait for the interface to see a 0 in the command word, then load a value of 41.  The time it takes the interface to see a 0 value is directly related to the RPI of the interface.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------]]>
</LocalizedComment>
</Comment>
<Text>
<![CDATA[EQU(AOI_Seq,10)XIC(RFID_In.Channel[Channel].Reset)OTU(RFID_Out.Channel[Channel].Reset)MOV(100,AOI_Seq);]]>
</Text>
</Rung>
</RLLContent>
</Routine>
</Routines>
